		<p class="text1">This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you visit or make a purchase from <a href="/" style="color:black">www.vitalityclub.in</a> (the “Site”).</p>
		
		<p class="text1 mb-0"><b>Personal Information We Collect</b></p>
